window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Elaine is ripped from this world to Pallos, a land of unlimited possibilities made real by a grand system governing classes, skills, and magic.</b></p> <p>An ideal society? <i>What is this, a fantasy novel</i>?</p> <p>Adventures? <i>Right this way!</i></p> <p>A grand quest? <i>Nah</i>.</p> <p>Friends and loot? <i>Heck yes</i>!</p> <p>Humans are the top dog? <i>Nope; dinosaur food</i>.</p> <p>Healing and fighting? <i>Well, everything is trying to eat her</i>.</p> <p>Join Elaine as she travels around Pallos, discovering all the wonders and mysteries of the world, trying to find a place where she belongs, hunting those elusive mangos, all while the ominous Dragoneye Moons watch her every move....</p>"; 
